      "csl:dictionary": "pwg",
      "csl:recordNumber": "52624",
      "csl:lineNumber": 509984,
      "csl:pageColumn": "5-0081",
      "rdf:value": "<L>52624<pc>5-0081<k1>bAhula<k2>bAhula\n{#bAhula#}¦\n<div n=\"1\"> 1) <ab>proparox.</ab> <lex>adj.</lex> von {#bahula#} <is>gaṇa</is> {#saMkalAdi#} zu <ls>P. 4,2,75.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 2) <lex>m.</lex> (von {#bahulA#} {%die Plejaden) der Monat%} <is>Kārttika</is>\n<ls>AK. 1,1,3,18.</ls>\n<ls>H. 155.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 3) <lex>m.</lex> {%Feuer%} (<ab>vgl.</ab> {#bahula)#}\n<ls>ŚABDAR.</ls> im <ls>ŚKDR.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 4) <lex>m.</lex> <ab>N. pr.</ab>\n[Page5-0082]\neines Fürsten\n<ls>VP. 386, N. 19.</ls>\neines Sohnes des <is>Śākyamuni</is>\n<ls>TRIK. 1,1,12.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 5) <lex>n.</lex> <ab>oxyt.</ab> <ab>nom. abstr.</ab> von {#bahula#} <is>gaṇa</is> {#pfTvAdi#} zu <ls>P. 5,1,122.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 6) <lex>n.</lex> (von {#bAhu)#} {%Armschiene%}\n<ls>H. 769.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 7) <ab>N. pr.</ab> einer Oertlichkeit in <is>Dakṣiṇāpatha</is>\n<ls>Verz. d. Oxf. H. 338,b,37.</ls>\n<LEND>"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AbAhula#record-pwk",
